01:12:41,566 --> 01:12:42,399
Take care.

1478
01:12:42,483 --> 01:12:43,733
Yeah, you too.

1479
01:12:48,239 --> 01:12:49,072
[sighs]

1480
01:12:52,869 --> 01:12:53,910
-Hi, baby.
