say he was coming on to them.

1487
01:13:07,925 --> 01:13:09,050
Les isn't gay.

1488
01:13:09,135 --> 01:13:10,427
How do we know that?

1489
01:13:10,511 --> 01:13:11,803
Because he isn't.

1490
01:13:12,763 --> 01:13:14,848
Levonne Willis is stirring the pot.

