1628
01:22:19,643 --> 01:22:20,476
Joe?

1629
01:22:22,521 --> 01:22:23,771
Something the matter?

1630
01:22:26,525 --> 01:22:28,985
[sighs] Nicky's in trouble.

1631
01:22:31,071 --> 01:22:32,864
