-That's out.
-That's out.

1654
01:24:10,254 --> 01:24:11,963
-Gonna do time, then.
-Right.

1655
01:24:12,047 --> 01:24:14,715
[Asteroid babbling]

1656
01:24:15,842 --> 01:24:17,218
Maybe this is hell.

1657
01:24:18,554 --> 01:24:20,429
No, if this was hell,

1658
01:24:20,514 --> 01:24:22,139
my mother would be here,

1659
01:24:22,683 --> 01:24:24,308
reading from USA Today

1660
01:24:24,393 --> 01:24:29,188
about which foods are the most
mucus-producing when you have a cold.

1661
01:24:30,065 --> 01:24:33,234
