and yelling in Spanish]

1687
01:26:09,623 --> 01:26:11,624
[firefighters yelling indistinctly]

1688
01:26:11,708 --> 01:26:13,167
[paramedic] Get the oxygen on her.

1689
01:26:13,251 --> 01:26:15,252
[Mrs. Ramirez continues screaming]

1690
