[firefighter 1] Any more up there?

1691
01:26:23,220 --> 01:26:26,764
[firefighter 2] Nothing we could see.
The 4th floor's too secluded.

1692
01:26:26,848 --> 01:26:28,182
[firefighter 1] Where were they?

1693
01:26:29,142 --> 01:26:31,143
[Mrs. Ramirez continues screaming]

