1706
01:27:09,391 --> 01:27:11,726
Help, help.

1707
01:27:11,810 --> 01:27:14,645
Help, we need help. Help.

1708
01:27:15,564 --> 01:27:17,022
Any messages for me?

1709
01:27:19,151 --> 01:27:21,360
We got bargains. We got deals.

1710
01:27:22,154 --> 01:27:24,071
All your electronics needs.

1711
01:27:24,740 --> 01:27:29,160
We got deals.
Under one roof. Under one roof.

1712
01:27:29,244 --> 01:27:31,620
Help, help. We need help.

1713
